data.description:
Welcome to this delightful single-story single-family home situated in a non-HOA community in Port St Lucie. This well-maintained residence features 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, offering a cozy and inviting living space.The stack bedroom design enhances privacy and functionality, making this home an ideal retreat for individuals and families alike. The attached 1-car garage provides convenience and security for your vehicle and storage needs.The interior showcases a laundry room equipped with a tub, ensuring practicality for everyday tasks. The kitchen is a focal point, boasting modern appliances and granite countertops, creating a stylish and efficient space for culinary pursuits. The family room provides a comfortable area for relaxation and entertainment, making it a central hub for socializing. The master bedroom is a serene haven, complete with a closet and ensuite bathroom for added convenience.

Step outside to discover a fenced backyard, offering both privacy and security. The outdoor space features a shed for additional storage and an open patio, providing the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.

This great home is strategically located just minutes away from fine shopping, dining, and various amenities, offering the perfect blend of convenience and comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your own and experience the best of Port St Lucie living.
